\ format ( … template -- string ) — positional {n} fill from the stack.
\ Plain string literals are raw; only format substitutes, and only {n}.

42 "value: {0}" format .
"foo" "name={0}" format .
1 2 3 "{0} {1} {2}" format .

\ non-numeric braces are left literal (no variable lookup)
"keep {x} literal" format .

\ a plain literal is raw — no substitution at all
"raw {0}" .
.s
